Reasoning: The paper deals with discrete dynamical systems and mathematical properties of such systems, which falls under the category of cs.DS (Discrete Mathematics). The concept of Integral Value Transformations (IVTs) and its application in Affine Discrete Dynamical Systems (ADDS) involves information theory and signal processing, which falls under the category of cs.IT (Information Theory). The Optimal Distributed and Parallel Environment (ODPE) designed in the paper involves system control and optimization, which falls under the category of cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves numerical analysis and optimization, which falls under the category of cs.SC (Numerical Analysis) and cs.NA (Optimization and Control).
